{
  "info": {
    "name": "hotel-sim · Scoped Payment Flow (room-on-auth + spa-upfront)",
    "_postman_id": "b7e1a0c2-9d4e-4c8a-9f2b-3a1c5e7d9f01",
    "description": "Proves the load-bearing Stage-4 payment design:\n\n  * The ROOM line sits on a held MANUAL authorisation (a card imprint at\n    check-in) that is NEVER captured here — capture is the not-yet-built\n    checkout step.\n  * The SPA line is added AFTER the room auth and settled by its OWN,\n    SEPARATE, IMMEDIATE payment, scoped to the spa line via lineCoverage\n    (WHK-016 / payment_line).\n  * Scoped allocation lands the spa revenue on the SPA line only — the room\n    line's revenuePosted stays 0 (auth != revenue; ledger posts on capture).\n\nThis is the baseline the checkout/completeLine slice will build on. When that\nslice lands, the new completion call slots in after folder 05 and re-asserts\nthe room line's revenuePosted flips 0 -> 54000.\n\nPREREQUISITES\n  1. core-api on {{baseUrl}}, payments-sim on {{pspBaseUrl}} (docker compose up).\n  2. payments-sim running with the 'test' profile (so /v1/test/... is live —\n     it stands in for the deferred pay-web customer checkout).\n  3. Products seeded:\n       docker compose exec -T db psql -U hotelops -d hotelops < seed-products.sql\n     (provides ROOM 1111… £180/night and SPA 3333… Couples Massage £80.)\n\nRun the whole collection top-to-bottom (Collection Runner or one request at a\ntime). Variables chain automatically.\n\nMoney is minor units (pence). Room £180 x 3 nights = 54000. Spa £80 = 8000.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8080" },
    { "key": "pspBaseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8081" },
    { "key": "humanAuthToken", "value": "operator-confirmed-poc-token" },
    { "key": "roomProductId", "value": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111" },
    { "key": "spaProductId", "value": "33333333-3333-3333-3333-333333333333" },
    { "key": "roomStartsAt", "value": "2026-07-01T15:00:00Z" },
    { "key": "roomEndsAt", "value": "2026-07-04T11:00:00Z" },
    { "key": "spaStartsAt", "value": "2026-07-02T14:00:00Z" },
    { "key": "spaEndsAt", "value": "2026-07-02T15:00:00Z" },
    { "key": "roomAmount", "value": "54000" },
    { "key": "spaAmount", "value": "8000" },
    { "key": "customerId", "value": "" },
